{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"566","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"企業促進員工工作生活平衡 最高補助60萬元","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>2019-11-12 15:12 </span><span style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>中央社 記者吳欣紜台北<span lang='EN-US'>12</span>日電</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Meiryo, 微軟正黑體; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Meiryo, 微軟正黑體; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>為了讓企業推動優於法令的友善員工措施，勞動部辦理「推動工作生活平衡補助計畫」，補助項目包含員工紓壓課程、兒童或長者臨時照顧空間等項目，最高補助新台幣60萬元。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Meiryo, 微軟正黑體; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Meiryo, 微軟正黑體; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>勞動部從民國103年起辦理「推動工作生活平衡補助計畫」，總計補助1442家企業辦理2334項友善員工措施，以支持員工紓解身心壓力，盼能促進員工及眷屬親子交流，約有42萬員工及家屬受益。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Meiryo, 微軟正黑體; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Meiryo, 微軟正黑體; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>勞動部今天舉行例行業務報告，勞動福祉退休司長孫碧霞表示，「推動工作生活平衡補助計畫」補助項目包含企業辦理員工關懷與協助課程、員工紓壓課程、友善家庭措施、兒童或長者臨時照顧空間、特殊需求員工協助措施及宣導等。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Meiryo, 微軟正黑體; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Meiryo, 微軟正黑體; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>其中有越來越多企業為協助員工職場適應，透過申請補助「員工關懷與協助」措施，辦理員工危機關懷、敏感度訓練、輔導關懷技巧等課程，培訓各級主管對員工關懷知能，建立企業關懷種子，給予有需要支持及協助的員工即時關懷。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Meiryo, 微軟正黑體; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Meiryo, 微軟正黑體; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>另外，由於高齡化時代來臨，在今年辦理的企業中，除了有設置兒童臨時照顧空間外，也有企業為協助員工就近照顧家中長輩，在企業內設置長者臨時照顧空間，當員工家中照顧者臨時無法照顧長輩時，可將家中長輩帶來公司就近照看，使員工兼顧工作及家庭照顧。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Meiryo, 微軟正黑體; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Meiryo, 微軟正黑體; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>孫碧霞指出，明年「推動工作與生活平衡補助計畫」第一次申請，預定在109年2至3月間受理，企業可提前評估員工需求，規劃工作與生活平衡措施或課程活動以申請補助。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Meiryo, 微軟正黑體; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Meiryo, 微軟正黑體; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>資料來源：https://money.udn.com/money/story/7307/4160095</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Meiryo, 微軟正黑體; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'>&nbsp;</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2019-11-14","clk_count":"135"}},"__N_SSG":true}